{
  "texts": [
    "• Evidence Quality indicates if the type of evidence requested in the query is present within the cited statements (e.g.",
    "functional assays in patient-derived cells).",
    "This score aims to penalize (1) uncited evidence and (2) evidence that is cited, but irrelevant.",
    "To demonstrate this, we provide an example response from DR Tulu that met the Evidence Synthesis criteria (Figure 23)",
    "• Evidence Support measures the proportion of cited statements in the response that are consistent with the original source text retrieved."
  ]
}